# Vectorized Expression Evaluation

## Description

SIMD-accelerated expression evaluation on column vectors. Supports arithmetic, comparisons, string operations.

## Implementation

```rust
pub fn simd_add_i64(a: &[i64], b: &[i64], result: &mut [i64]) {
    #[cfg(target_feature = "avx2")]
    unsafe {
        for i in (0..a.len()).step_by(4) {
            let va = _mm256_loadu_si256(a.as_ptr().add(i) as *const __m256i);
            let vb = _mm256_loadu_si256(b.as_ptr().add(i) as *const __m256i);
            let vr = _mm256_add_epi64(va, vb);
            _mm256_storeu_si256(result.as_mut_ptr().add(i) as *mut __m256i, vr);
        }
    }
}
```

## Cost Model

- SIMD speedup: 4-8x
- Vectorized: add, sub, mul, cmp, etc.

## References

1. Polychroniou et al., "Efficient Lightweight Compression", DaMoN 2015
